# Launch site is self-contained (no CDN): its og card + favicons must travel.
!site/**/*.png
# Brand/icon assets (app-icon iconset + previews, labyrinth marks) must travel.
!assets/**/*.png
# Icon Composer app-icon layer images must travel with the repo (actool needs them).
!macos/M1K3.icon/Assets/**
!app/3d/**/*.png
# Durable project memory should travel with the repo, even though the global
# gitignore ignores all of .claude/. Anchored re-include (the prior knowledge-server project pattern).
!/.claude/
/.claude/*
!/.claude/project-memory.md
# Archived project-memory blocks travel too (split off when the live file grows).
!/.claude/project-memory-archive-*.md
# Project skills are repo tooling (like the tracked agents/ + commands/) — they
# document this codebase's pipelines, so they travel with it.
!/.claude/skills/
!/.claude/skills/**

# --- Private runtime data: must NEVER be committed (access-readiness) ---
