tests/unified-suite/output/
scripts/test_report.json
data/test-results/

# graphify knowledge graph: generated/regenerable (~18M), goes stale on edits.
# Collaborators run `graphify update .` locally; CLAUDE.md rules are conditional
# on graphify-out/ existing. The .graphifyignore config + skill ARE tracked.
graphify-out/
